    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！　この間話してくれた\nゲーム会社さんの企画って、どうなりました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}! About that project\nfrom the game company‚ what happened with it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ここのゲーム会社さん、もし恋の時も面白い企画を\n持ってきてくれたので気になってるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This company brought us such a fun project\nfor \"Moshi-Koi‚\" so I've been curious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その件か。ちょうど昨日の夜にテーマと\nメンバーの割り振りについて連絡が届いていたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that. I just got word last night about\nthe theme and member assignments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.126893266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "メンバーの組み合わせはすみれ、瑠依、千紗、渚だ\n瑠依もいるし、他のメンバーとも仲良くやれそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The group consists of you‚ Rui‚ Chisa‚ and Nagisa.\nWith Rui there‚ I'm sure you'll all get along fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.6741496722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　もし恋の時みたいに\nまた渚さんと共演出来るなんて嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'm so happy to work with\nNagisa-san again‚ just like in \"Moshi-Koi\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3408163388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "それでそれで、私達のテーマは\nどんなテーマなんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ so‚ what exactly is\nour theme going to be!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5408163388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.6741496722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "雪が降る田舎に住んでいる女の子の\n青春ラブストーリーとかでしょうか……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it something like a youth love story\nabout a girl living in the snowy countryside…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3408163388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それはよく分からないが……\nラブストーリーというテーマは一致しているぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not so sure about that‚ but…\nit does fall under the romance theme.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
